body_html: @kwotsin I tried it and you are right the Fatal signal 11 (SIGSEGV), code 1 error is resolved, but overall there is no change in either accuracy or performance. However the interesting thing is that the model size inreased from 2.3MB to around 6MB.Though the output is the same. AFAIK quantize_nodes is the differentiator in terms of performance..
